snippet.title: Superliminal | Announce Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
"Superliminal is coming to Playstation on April, 2020.

In this mind-bending first-person puzzler, you wake up in a dream with the power to resize things based on perspective. Things get weirder and weirder as you look for a way out of this dream therapy program that’s supposed to make you better."
